<para>Detailed documentation for the bsm_4tops event class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
    </detaileddescription>
    <programlisting>
<codeline lineno="1"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="2"><highlight class="comment">/**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="3"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@file<sp/>event.dox</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="4"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Detailed<sp/>documentation<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>bsm_4tops<sp/>event<sp/>class.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="5"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@page<sp/>bsm_4tops_event_page<sp/>bsm_4tops<sp/>Event</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>bsm_4tops_event_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`bsm_4tops`<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>specialization<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>and<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>handle<sp/>events<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>4-top-quark<sp/>analysis<sp/>(BSM).<sp/>It<sp/>defines<sp/>the<sp/>structure<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event,<sp/>including<sp/>the<sp/>particles<sp/>and<sp/>their<sp/>relationships,<sp/>and<sp/>provides<sp/>methods<sp/>for<sp/>building<sp/>and<sp/>compiling<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>input<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>bsm_4tops_event_class<sp/>The<sp/>bsm_4tops<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`bsm_4tops`<sp/>class<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>and<sp/>implements<sp/>its<sp/>virtual<sp/>methods<sp/>to<sp/>provide<sp/>event-specific<sp/>functionality.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>bsm_4tops_event_ctor<sp/>Constructor<sp/>and<sp/>Destructor</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`bsm_4tops()`:<sp/>The<sp/>constructor<sp/>initializes<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>by<sp/>setting<sp/>its<sp/>name,<sp/>defining<sp/>the<sp/>data<sp/>leaves<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>read<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>input<sp/>tree,<sp/>and<sp/>registering<sp/>the<sp/>particle<sp/>types<sp/>that<sp/>are<sp/>expected<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`~bsm_4tops()`:<sp/>The<sp/>destructor<sp/>cleans<sp/>up<sp/>any<sp/>resources<sp/>allocated<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>bsm_4tops_event_methods<sp/>Methods</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`event_template*<sp/>clone()`:<sp/>Creates<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>instance<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>`bsm_4tops`<sp/>event.<sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>used<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>framework<sp/>to<sp/>create<sp/>copies<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>for<sp/>parallel<sp/>processing.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`void<sp/>build(element_t*<sp/>el)`:<sp/>Populates<sp/>the<sp/>event&apos;s<sp/>data<sp/>members<sp/>(event<sp/>number,<sp/>pile-up,<sp/>missing<sp/>transverse<sp/>energy,<sp/>etc.)<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>input<sp/>data<sp/>element.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`void<sp/>CompileEvent()`:<sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>core<sp/>method<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>class.<sp/>It<sp/>reconstructs<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>by<sp/>linking<sp/>the<sp/>various<sp/>particles<sp/>together.<sp/>This<sp/>includes:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Sorting<sp/>the<sp/>particles<sp/>by<sp/>their<sp/>index.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Associating<sp/>top<sp/>children<sp/>with<sp/>their<sp/>parent<sp/>tops.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Linking<sp/>truth<sp/>jets<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>constituent<sp/>tops.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Matching<sp/>truth<sp/>jet<sp/>partons<sp/>to<sp/>truth<sp/>jets<sp/>and<sp/>top<sp/>children.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Linking<sp/>reconstructed<sp/>jets<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>constituent<sp/>tops.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Matching<sp/>reconstructed<sp/>jet<sp/>partons<sp/>to<sp/>jets<sp/>and<sp/>top<sp/>children.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Matching<sp/>leptons<sp/>(electrons<sp/>and<sp/>muons)<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>corresponding<sp/>top<sp/>children.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Vectorizing<sp/>the<sp/>particle<sp/>collections<sp/>for<sp/>easier<sp/>access.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>bsm_4tops_event_particles<sp/>Particle<sp/>Collections</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`bsm_4tops`<sp/>event<sp/>contains<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>particle<sp/>collections:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_Tops`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>top<sp/>quarks<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_Children`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>decay<sp/>products<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>top<sp/>quarks.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="35"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_TruthJets`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>truth-level<sp/>jets.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="36"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_TruthJetParton`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>partons<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>truth<sp/>jets.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_Jets`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>reconstructed<sp/>jets.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_JetParton`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>partons<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>reconstructed<sp/>jets.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_Electrons`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>electrons<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="40"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_Muons`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>muons<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="41"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="42"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>After<sp/>`CompileEvent()`<sp/>is<sp/>called,<sp/>these<sp/>maps<sp/>are<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>populate<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>vector<sp/>collections<sp/>for<sp/>easier<sp/>access:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="43"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Tops`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="44"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Children`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="45"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`TruthJets`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="46"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Jets`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="47"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Electrons`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="48"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Muons`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="49"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`DetectorObjects`<sp/>(a<sp/>combined<sp/>collection<sp/>of<sp/>jets,<sp/>muons,<sp/>and<sp/>electrons)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="50"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*/</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
    </programlisting>
